title: [DVD-R].Comfy.My.Home.iso
description:
My Home offers toddlers hours of delight while exploring the home environment through a variety of day-to-day activities. The game is full of songs and surprises through which toddlers learn about the importance of tidiness, to recognize objects through sounds and voices and how to dress appropriately according to the weather. With Didi, a cute 3 year old girl and her friends, toddlers will enjoy playing hide and seek among other exciting activities.

The software package includes "My Home" overlay.

Developmental Benefits:

Expands vocabulary and language skills.
Explores the home environment.
Develops creative and thinking skills.
Teaches cause and effect.
Teaches the relationship between comparative concepts.

Ages: 1-3 years 
Level: Intermediate 
Available langugaes: English (US), English (UK), Spanish (L. America), French, German, Dutch, Norwegian, Swedish, Danish, Polish, Russian, Arabic, Hebrew, Finnish
